{
  "stem": "628.5",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I said to the Polish here in the reservation, I said, I'm coming from the 24th to the 25th.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Have you got a vacancy then?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I book a room there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So my wife said, you-- I said, no, don't worry, once I have a room there, I stay there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They have to sling me out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came over.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got the room.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't have the invitation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have nothing, you see.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's why I'm here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's why I'm telling you today that story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It has to be--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yesterday.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yesterday was my anniversary-- not anniversary.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My-- how do you call it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] my-- because I don't-- I don't call it a liberation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Russians, they didn't liberate nobody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's a year too late they came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then there should be 2, 3 million people more in the world.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because these 2,000 they found there, it was like, you know, the rest, they couldn't even use them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "No liberation for me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was as-- yesterday that meeting was from everywhere the Yiddish people came, from all over the world to remember the 6 million, to say kaddish, to give them our blessing.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were there, one family, strong in our hands-- and didn't know what's going to happen to us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Poland-- anything can happen in Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They could have thrown bombs there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we did go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Today, it's what's it called?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a fantasy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Politically.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Today, they want to show the world today.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They want to show the world-- kings were there, and diplomats were there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What they come to do there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What did they come to do there?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To excuse themself?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "To say, we are sorry?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
